<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,289,1848,1873]" pageId="1" pageNumber="474">Description</emphasis>
. Body length (including tegmina), male: 
<quantity box="[753,884,1848,1873]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.35" metricValueMax="6.4" metricValueMin="6.3" pageId="1" pageNumber="474" unit="mm" value="6.35" valueMax="6.4" valueMin="6.3">6.3–6.4mm</quantity>
; female: 
<quantity box="[986,1118,1848,1872]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="8.0" metricValueMax="8.1" metricValueMin="7.9" pageId="1" pageNumber="474" unit="mm" value="8.0" valueMax="8.1" valueMin="7.9">7.9–8.1mm</quantity>
